    <item>
      <title>美国原油的加入改变了世界上最重要的石油价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/world-s-most-important-oil-price-transformed-by-adding-us-crude</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过多年的怀疑、批评和交易员的愤怒之后，由于来自德克萨斯州西部的原油的注入，世界上最重要的石油价格比以往任何时候都表现得更好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/world-s-most-important-oil-price-transformed-by-adding-us-crude</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
