      <title>印尼卢比疲软导致外国投资者可能继续撤离印尼股市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-03/exodus-of-foreign-investors-from-indonesian-stocks-may-continue-amid-weak-rupiah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在央行意外加息对提振印尼货币的影响微乎其微之后，全球基金准备继续抛售印尼股票。]]></description>
